<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Dallas Roofing & Insurance Restoration | Free Roof Inspection</title>

  <meta name="description" content="Dallas roofing specialists in storm damage and insurance restoration. Get a free roof inspection and help with your insurance claim." />

  <meta name="keywords" content="Dallas roofing, roof repair Dallas, storm damage roof, insurance roof claim, roof inspection Dallas" />

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #111;
    }

    header {
      padding: 80px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: white;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background: #f59e0b;
      color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      background: #f3f4f6;
    }

    input, select {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }

    button {
      padding: 12px;
      width: 100%;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>Dallas Roofing & Insurance Restoration Specialists</h1>
  <p>We inspect storm damage, document your roof, and help maximize your insurance claim approval.</p>
  <a href="#contact" class="btn">Get Free Roof Inspection</a>
  <p style="margin-top:15px;font-size:0.9rem;">
    ✔ Free inspection ✔ Insurance claim help ✔ Local Dallas experts
  </p>
</header>

<section>
  <h2>Roofing Services</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">Storm Damage Roof Inspection</div>
    <div class="card">Insurance Claim Assistance</div>
    <div class="card">Roof Repair</div>
    <div class="card">Roof Replacement</div>
    <div class="card">Emergency Leak Repair</div>
    <div class="card">Hail Damage Assessment</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Our Process</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Free Roof Inspection</li>
    <li>Damage Documentation</li>
    <li>Insurance Claim Support</li>
    <li>Repair or Replacement</li>
  </ol>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Common Roof Issues in Dallas</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Hail damage not visible from the ground</li>
    <li>Missing or lifted shingles after storms</li>
    <li>Leaks causing interior damage</li>
    <li>Insurance underpayment or denied claims</li>
    <li>Old or deteriorating roofing systems</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Why Homeowners Choose Us</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Local Dallas roofing specialists</li>
    <li>Insurance claim guidance included</li>
    <li>Fast response after storms</li>
    <li>Honest inspections with photo evidence</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Is Your Roof Damaged Without You Knowing?</h2>
  <p>Storm damage is often invisible from the ground. Small issues can turn into costly repairs if ignored.</p>
  <a href="#contact" class="btn">Request Free Inspection</a>
</section>

<section id="contact">
  <h2>Request Free Roof Inspection</h2>

  <form>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" required />
    <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" required />
    <input type="text" placeholder="Property Address" required />

    <select>
      <option>Storm Damage</option>
      <option>Leak</option>
      <option>Full Replacement</option>
      <option>Insurance Claim Help</option>
    </select>

    <button type="submit">Get Inspection</button>
  </form>

  <p style="font-size:0.9rem;margin-top:10px;">
    We respond within 24 hours.
  </p>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Dallas Roofing Partners. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>